<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to LinkedIn Clone</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #0077B5, #00A0DC);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }

    .header img {
      width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: white;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #0077B5;
    }

    .info-box {
      background-color: #f3f6f8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .info-box p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .info-box ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .cta a {
      background-color: #0077B5;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/linkedin-logo_578229-227.jpg" alt="linkedIn Clone Logo">
    <h1>Welcome to LinkedIn Clone!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p class="greeting"><strong>Hello <%= name %>,</strong></p>
    <p>We're thrilled to have you join our professional community! Linked Clone is your platform to connect, learn, and grow in your career.</p>
    <div class="info-box">
      <p><strong>Here's how to get started:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Complete your profile</li>
        <li>Connect with colleagues and friends</li>
        <li>Join groups relevant to your interests</li>
        <li>Explore job opportunities</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="<%= profileUrl %>">Complete Your Profile</a>
    </div>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The LinkedIn Clone Team</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>